replies.body:
Inconsistencies in latency (ping) are usually caused by routing issues to the server or by network settings that don't provide a stable connection to the League servers. We can investigate your route, but as a first step, I recommend ensuring your local network settings are cool with our [connection guide. 
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if you still encounter high latency after working through those steps.
